cial Minecraft Education blog provides updates, community news, and support for educators using Minecraft in the classroom.\n\nIn conclusion, Minecraft offers a unique opportunity to bring game-based learning into the classroom and engage students in new ways. By exploring the benefits of Minecraft Education and incorporating it into various subjects and activities, educators can help foster creativity, collaboration,", "quality_score": 80, "orchestrator_error": null, "model_used": "ollama/mistral", "seo_title": "Minecraft and education", "seo_description": "Minecraft and Education: Unlocking the Potential of Gaming for Learning\n======================================================================", "seo_keywords": "[\"minecraft\", \"students\", \"skills\", \"learning\", \"education\"]", "stage": "pending", "percentage": 0, "category": "blog_post", "style": "educational", "tone": "academic", "target_audience": "General", "target_length": 3000, "estimated_cost": 0.0, "featured_image_url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/3977908/pexels-photo-3977908.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940"}', 'ollama/mistral', 80, NULL, NULL, '2026-01-27 17:39:23.020115', '2026-01-27 17:41:16.773385', NULL, 'pending_human_review', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'content-agent', NULL, 'General', 'blog_post', NULL, '{"metadata": {"published_at": "2026-01-27T17:41:16.773385+00:00", "published_by": "dev_user_local"}}', 'Minecraft and education', 'Minecraft and Education: Unlocking the Potential of Gaming for Learning
