a digital drawing tablet, or a pottery class.\n*   **Were you constantly making up stories, putting on plays with your stuffed animals?** This could point to creative writing, joining a local improv group, or even starting a Dungeons & Dragons campaign with friends.\n*   **Did you love taking things apart to see how they worked?** Maybe you\u2019d find joy in repairing old electronics, tinkering with a Raspberry Pi, or learning basic car maintenance.\n\nDon\u2019t judge the answers. The goal isn''t to find a new career; it''s to find a thread of genuine, unadulterated interest. The thing you did just because it lit up your brain.\n\n### Conduct a \"Curiosity Audit\"\n\nIf the childhood well feels dry, let''s move to the present. Your current patterns of attention are a treasure map pointing toward", "seo_title": "doing things you love", "seo_description": "doing things you love. I found it in a dusty corner of the closet, tucked behind a stack of old yearbooks and a box of cables for electronics I no longe...", "seo_keywords": ["your", "that", "love", "this", "with"], "topic": "doing things you love", "style": "narrative", "tone": "casual", "category": "blog_post", "target_audience": "General", "post_id": null, "quality_score": 7.498045586978421, "content_length": 8085, "word_count": 1381}', 'Google Gemini (gemini-2.5-pro)', 7, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-03 01:49:18.776504', '2026-02-03 01:50:48.224155', NULL, 'pending_human_review', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'content-agent', NULL, 'General', 'blog_post', NULL, '{"metadata": {"published_at": "2026-02-03T01:50:48.223652+00:00", "published_by": "mock_user_12345"}}', 'doing things you love', 'doing things you love. I found it in a dusty corner of the closet, tucked behind a stack of old yearbooks and a box of cables for electronics I no longe...', '["your", "that", "love", "this", "with"]', 'pending', 0, NULL, NULL, '{"draft": "gemini-gemini-pro", "assess": "gemini-gemini-pro", "refine": "gemini-gemini-pro", "outline": "gemini-gemini-pro", "finalize": "gemini-gemini-pro", "research": "gemini-gemini-pro"}', 'balanced', 0.000000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Embracing Passion: The Beauty of Playing Rusty Strings', '{"draft": "Google Gemini (gemini-2.5-pro)"}', '{"decision_tree": {"gemini_error": null, "gemini_attempted": true, "gemini_succeeded": true, "ollama_available": false, "gemini_key_available": true, "huggingface_token_available": false}, "skipped_ollama": true, "requested_model": "gemini-pro", "requested_provider": "gemini", "attempted_providers": ["gemini"]}', NULL);
